Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.17,0:22:54.84,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奇异的独角戏舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.84,0:22:57.51,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用你的眼睛看着 竞争
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.56,0:23:02.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fad(200,200)}遗落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.51,0:23:02.60,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}欺骗吧 Close Enough
