Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.17,0:23:28.25,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}带有偏见的分类
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.25,0:23:30.46,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要相信没有故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.46,0:23:32.51,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道你准备好了
